      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">駟驖.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>駟驖孔阜，六轡在手。公之媚子，從公于狩。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>His four iron-black horses are in very fine condition;
The six reins are in the hand of the charioteer.
The ruler's favourites
Follow him to the chase.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
