      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">駟驖.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>奉時辰牡，辰牡孔碩。公曰左之，舍拔則獲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The male animals of the season are made to present themselves,
The males in season, of very large size.
The ruler says, 'To the left of them;'
Then he lets go his arrows and hits.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
