      <prop type="x-translation-ref">駟驖.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>遊于北園，四馬既閑。輶車鸞鑣，載獫歇驕。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He rambles in the northern park;
His four horses display their training.
Light carriages, with bells at the horses' bits,
Convey the long and short-mouthed dogs.</seg>
      </tuv>
